Gold Futures Top $1,550 an Ounce, Rise to Two-week High on Comex in N.Y.

-- B y   P a t r i c k   M c K i e r n a n
-- 
2011-07-11T12:23:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/gold-futures-top-1-550-an-ounce-rise-to-two-week-high-on-comex-in-n-y-.html
Gold futures for August delivery
rose $12.20, or 0.8 percent, to $1,553.80 an ounce at 8:21 a.m.
on the Comex in  New York . Earlier, the metal reached $1,554.40,
the highest for a most-active contract since June 22. The price
reached a record $1,577.40 on May 2.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Patrick McKiernan at 
 pmckiernan@bloomberg.net  